r: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 13px; border-bottom-right-radius: 13px; box-shadow: none; display: block; font-weight: normal; flex-direction: unset; float: unset; height: auto; justify-content: unset; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; overflow-x: unset; overflow-y: unset; padding-top: 3px; padding-bottom: 5px; padding-left: 5px; padding-right: 5px; position: relative; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; text-shadow: none; transform: none; width: auto; -webkit-box-reflect: unset;\">WGCNA 简介及其在基因相关网络分析中的应用</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h1> \n<figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center;\"> \n <img src=\"https://files.mdnice.com/user/58457/816774ef-4321-447b-b14c-78624a6ec0cd.png\" alt style=\"display: block; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; max-width: 100%; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 16px; border-top-right-radius: 16px; border-bottom-right-radius: 16px; border-bottom-left-radius: 16px; object-fit: fill; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px;\"> \n</figure> \n<h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; align-items: unset; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: unset; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-left-width: 1px; border-right-width: 1px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; box-shadow: none; display: block; flex-direction: unset; float: unset; height: auto; justify-content: unset; line-height: 1.5em; overflow-x: unset; overflow-y: unset; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; position: relative; text-align: left; text-shadow: none; transform: none; width: auto; -webkit-box-reflect: unset;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 10px; padding-right: 0px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: solid; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-left-width: 5px; border-right-width: 1px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-color: rgb(248, 57, 41); border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; align-items: unset; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: unset; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; box-shadow: none; display: block; font-weight: bold; flex-direction: unset; float: unset; height: auto; justify-content: unset; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; overflow-x: unset; overflow-y: unset; position: relative; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; text-shadow: none; transform: none; width: auto; -webkit-box-reflect: unset;\">Introduction</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h2> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(53, 53, 53); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">加权基因共表达网络分析（WGCNA）是一种强大的一体化分析方法，使生物学家能够了解系统中所有基因的转录组范围关系，而不是孤立地了解每个基因。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(53, 53, 53); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">WGCNA 能够识别表现出相关性的特征集群（模块），并评估不同集群之间的关系。重要的是，WGCNA 还提供了模块与外部性状之间关联的数据，例如记录的样本表型。基因相关网络鉴定的基因具有很高的生物学相关性，因为同一模块内的基因可以共享调控机制，并在细胞和细胞间的分子通路内具有功能相关性。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(53, 53, 53); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">WGCNA 还可以为候选生物标记物和治疗药物提供信息。尽管 WGCNA 主要应用于转录组数据，但其原理适用于其他组学，例如甲基化数据。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(53, 53, 53); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">但是 WGCNA 是如何工作的，您可以在下一次 RNA-seq 研究中获得什么，它的局限性是什么？</p> \n<h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; align-items: unset; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: unset; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-left-width: 1px; border-right-width: 1px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; box-shadow: none; display: block; flex-direction: unset; float: unset; height: auto; justify-content: unset; line-height: 1.5em; overflow-x: unset; overflow-y: unset; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; position: relative; text-align: left; text-shadow: none; transform: none; width: auto; -webkit-box-reflect: unset;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 10px; padding-right: 0px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: solid; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-left-width: 5px; border-right-width: 1px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-color: rgb(248, 57, 41); border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; align-items: unset; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: unset; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; box-shadow: none; display: block; font-weight: bold; flex-direction: unset; float: unset; height: auto; justify-content: unset; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; overflow-x: unset; overflow-y: unset; position: relative; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; text-shadow: none; transform: none; width: auto; -webkit-box-reflect: unset;\">What is WGCNA?</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h2> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(53, 53, 53); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">WGCNA 是研究人员用来分析大量样本中复杂数据模式的系统生物学方法。WGCNA 分为四个主要的分析步骤：</p> \n<ol data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 25px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> \n <li> \n  <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n    加权基因相关网络的构建。 \n  </section></li> \n <li> \n  <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n    共表达模块的鉴定。 \n  </section></li> \n <li> \n  <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n    基因与样本性状的关联 \n  </section></li> \n <li> \n  <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n    推断作为表型候选驱动因素的模块内关键基因 \n  </section></li> \n</ol> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(53, 53, 53); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">WGCNA 通过基因或模块之间的成对相关性来确定这些结果，即从基因在网络的近邻中获取有关该基因的信息。不过，WGCNA 有很多选项和输出，对于对分析和生成的图谱了解有限的人来说，可能会有点困难。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(53, 53, 53); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">在此，我们将 WGCNA 方法、图谱及其解释分解成小块，供生物信息学专业知识有限的研究人员使用。</p> \n<h1 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"border-top-color: rgb(248, 57, 41); margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; align-items: unset; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: unset; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 2px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-left-width: 1px; border-right-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; box-shadow: none; display: flex; flex-direction: unset; float: unset; height: auto; justify-content: center; line-height: 1.5em; overflow-x: unset; overflow-y: unset; position: relative; text-align: center; text-shadow: none; transform: none; width: auto; -webkit-box-reflect: unset;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" style=\"font-size: 20px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(248, 57, 41); line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; align-items: unset; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-left-width: 1px; border-right-width: 1px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 13px; border-bottom-right-radius: 13px; box-shadow: none; display: block; font-weight: normal; flex-direction: unset; float: unset; height: auto; justify-content: unset; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; overflow-x: unset; overflow-y: unset; padding-top: 3px; padding-bottom: 5px; padding-left: 5px; padding-right: 5px; position: relative; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; text-shadow: none; transform: none; width: auto; -webkit-box-reflect: unset;\">WGCNA 的四个主要步骤</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h1> \n<h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; align-items: unset; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: unset; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-left-width: 1px; border-right-width: 1px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; box-shadow: none; display: block; flex-direction: unset; float: unset; height: auto; justify-content: unset; line-height: 1.5em; overflow-x: unset; overflow-y: unset; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; position: relative; text-align: left; text-shadow: none; transform: none; width: auto; -webkit-box-reflect: unset;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 10px; padding-right: 0px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: solid; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-left-width: 5px; border-right-width: 1px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-color: rgb(248, 57, 41); border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; align-items: unset; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: unset; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; box-shadow: none; display: block; font-weight: bold; flex-direction: unset; float: unset; height: auto; justify-content: unset; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; overflow-x: unset; overflow-y: unset; position: relative; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; text-shadow: none; transform: none; width: auto; -webkit-box-reflect: unset;\">1. 构建基因的加权相关网络</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h2> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(53, 53, 53); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">通常，WGCNA 从一个数据矩阵开始，该矩阵具有每个样本的基因表达。测量样本中基因之间的成对相关性。每个基因对的相关分数表明它们表达模式的相似性，并可能表明它们的潜在功能关系。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(53, 53, 53); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">WGCNA 的“加权”是旨在放大强相关性和弱相关性之间的差异，方法是将相关性提高到用户定义的幂级别来放大数据，高相关性表示基因强相连，而低相关性表示弱连接。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(53, 53, 53); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">然后，这些放大的加权相关值可以更轻松地在后续步骤中识别具有相似功能的基因集。如下面的网络图，其中基因由圆圈（称为节点）表示，加权相关系数的强度由连接两个基因的线（或边）的粗细表示。在下图中，SVOP 和 AMER3 之间的绿色粗线表示强相关性，因此，这两个基因之间存在潜在关联（Figure 1）。</p> \n<figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center;\"> \n <img src=\"https://files.mdnice.com/user/58457/3b1e5bc7-5b78-49b6-8c38-f421356d6955.png\" alt style=\"display: block; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; max-width: 100%; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 16px; border-top-right-radius: 16px; border-bottom-right-radius: 16px; border-bottom-left-radius: 16px; object-fit: fill; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px;\"> \n</figure> \n<h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; align-items: unset; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: unset; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-left-width: 1px; border-right-width: 1px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; box-shadow: none; display: block; flex-direction: unset; float: unset; height: auto; justify-content: unset; line-height: 1.5em; overflow-x: unset; overflow-y: unset; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; position: relative; text-align: left; text-shadow: none; transform: none; width: auto; -webkit-box-reflect: unset;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 10px; padding-right: 0px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: solid; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-left-width: 5px; border-right-width: 1px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-color: rgb(248, 57, 41); border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; align-items: unset; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: unset; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; box-shadow: none; display: block; font-weight: bold; flex-direction: unset; float: unset; height: auto; justify-content: unset; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; overflow-x: unset; overflow-y: unset; position: relative; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; text-shadow: none; transform: none; width: auto; -webkit-box-reflect: unset;\">2. 将网络划分为模块</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h2> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(53, 53, 53); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">WGCNA 使用网络的加权相关系数信息将表现出显著相似表达谱的基因放入称为模块的集合中。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(53, 53, 53); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">如果基因与网络中的许多共享节点基因具有相似的相关性，或者它们的网络节点有很大的重叠，则这些基因可能具有相似的表达模式，并且可以分组到同一个模块中。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(53, 53, 53); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">为了确定模块，对基因相关网络数据执行分层聚类。生成树状图，其中每个分支标识一个特定的模块（Figure 2）。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(53, 53, 53); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">可以采用动态树切割等方法来确定包含具有相似表达模式的基因的离散模块。每个模块都分配有不同的 ID 和颜色。“剪切树状图”时要小心，因为使用不当可能会扭曲聚类结果。然后，在下一个分析步骤中，这些簇用于识别与样品不同表型特征的任何关联。</p> \n<figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center;\"> \n <img src=\"https://files.mdnice.com/user/58457/daefbc13-7de9-4d89-820c-9d23feca9a82.png\" alt style=\"display: block; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; max-width: 100%; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 16px; border-top-right-radius: 16px; border-bottom-right-radius: 16px; border-bottom-left-radius: 16px; object-fit: fill; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px;\"> \n</figure> \n<h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; align-items: unset; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: unset; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-left-width: 1px; border-right-width: 1px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; box-shadow: none; display: block; flex-direction: unset; float: unset; height: auto; justify-content: unset; line-height: 1.5em; overflow-x: unset; overflow-y: unset; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; position: relative; text-align: left; text-shadow: none; transform: none; width: auto; -webkit-box-reflect: unset;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 10px; padding-right: 0px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: solid; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-left-width: 5px; border-right-width: 1px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-color: rgb(248, 57, 41); border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; align-items: unset; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: unset; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; box-shadow: none; display: block; font-weight: bold; flex-direction: unset; float: unset; height: auto; justify-content: unset; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; overflow-x: unset; overflow-y: unset; position: relative; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; text-shadow: none; transform: none; width: auto; -webkit-box-reflect: unset;\">3. 将表型性状与不同的基因模块相关联</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h2> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(53, 53, 53); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">使用树状图定义模块后，必须将输出简化为每个模块一个值，称为模块 eigengene。eigengene 是主成分分析的第一个成分，代表模块的整体表达。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(53, 53, 53); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">由于模块特征基因（module eigengene）将每个模块表征为一个单独的实体，因此我们能够对模块之间进行相关性分析，找出具有相似表达行为的模块，或确定每个模块与表型之间的相关性。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(53, 53, 53); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">例如，我们下面的示例显示 ME1 和 ME4 的模块特征基因高度相关，表明它们的生物学功能或样本来源类型可能相关（Figure 3A）。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(53, 53, 53); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">为了确定这两个模块是否具有相似的生物学作用，我们接下来可以测量每个模块的特征基因与不同患者特征、样本类型或疾病结果的相关程度。这些生物变量可能包括患者的年龄、性别或体重，缓解或死亡等结果，或者样本是来自健康患者还是疾病患者，或来自不同器官或肿瘤位置。研究人员利用这种方法确定了许多疾病的关键模块，如胶质母细胞瘤、乳腺癌和结直肠癌。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(53, 53, 53); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">在我们的示例中，ME1 和 ME4 都与健康样本高度相关，而 ME2 和 ME3 与胶质母细胞瘤样本高度相关（图 3B）。这表明这些模块中包含的基因可能在胶质母细胞瘤中发挥作用。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(53, 53, 53); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">我们可以通过进行基因本体（GO富集分析）分析来确定富含与特定途径或功能相关的基因的模块，从而了解这种可能性。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(53, 53, 53); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">但是，们还不知道每个模块中的哪些基因可能是最重要的。</p> \n<figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center;\"> \n <img src=\"https://files.mdnice.com/user/58457/8207feb0-4996-4675-a5e7-30b6c2a6bf4f.png\" alt style=\"display: block; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; max-width: 100%; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 16px; border-top-right-radius: 16px; border-bottom-right-radius: 16px; border-bottom-left-radius: 16px; object-fit: fill; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px;\"> \n</figure> \n<h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; align-items: unset; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: unset; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-left-width: 1px; border-right-width: 1px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; box-shadow: none; display: block; flex-direction: unset; float: unset; height: auto; justify-content: unset; line-height: 1.5em; overflow-x: unset; overflow-y: unset; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; position: relative; text-align: left; text-shadow: none; transform: none; width: auto; -webkit-box-reflect: unset;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 10px; padding-right: 0px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: solid; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-left-width: 5px; border-right-width: 1px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-color: rgb(248, 57, 41); border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; align-items: unset; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: unset; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; box-shadow: none; display: block; font-weight: bold; flex-direction: unset; float: unset; height: auto; justify-content: unset; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; overflow-x: unset; overflow-y: unset; position: relative; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; text-shadow: none; transform: none; width: auto; -webkit-box-reflect: unset;\">4. 识别潜在的驱动基因</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h2> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(53, 53, 53); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">最后，一旦我们确定了感兴趣的模块，我们就可以更深入地研究每个模块，以找到可能是特定性状的关键因素或可能影响该模块中其他基因的基因。每个模块可能包含许多基因;确定所谓的“枢纽基因（Hub genes）”进一步研究的理想候选者是至关重要的。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(53, 53, 53); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">枢纽基因被确定为模块中连接性最强的基因，并且预期与感兴趣的表型最密切相关。基因的表达也用于计算“Module membership”，它衡量基因在表达网络中特定模块的表达谱的程度。因此，Module membership 是确定基因优先级以进行进一步研究的有用工具。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(53, 53, 53); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">如果相关性高，并且在网络中连接良好，则该基因可能代表模块作为一个整体的整体表达。同样，该基因与目标性状的高度相关性进一步加强了其作为该模块重要驱动因素的可能性。</p>",
